es. The best fit is obtained for the explosion date as 2012\nMarch 15.3 UT.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 14 Nov 2013 16:31:24 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 8 Jan 2014 07:47:08 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-06-17"}
