 nanowire failure and\nstructure, and also demonstrate that GPU computing is an excellent tool for\nstudies requiring a large number independent trajectories in order to fully\ncharacterize a system's behavior.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 15 Nov 2013 15:54:37 GMT"}],"update_date":"2013-11-18"}
